ce8742b886df23878a16cadb"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p lang="ja" dir="ltr">桑巴巴士逃离 GT Auto <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/GT7?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#GT7</a> <a href="https://t.co/P0pciGU4A2">pic.twitter.com/P0pciGU4A2</a></p> - Pow_R(SUPRA_GT) (@powarmor0911) <a href="https://twitter.com/powarmor0911/status/1816431303618875420?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 7 月 25 日</a></blockquote></div><p>这显然是一个奇怪的 z 轴编程错误，但 Gran Turismo 的团队已经意识到这个问题并正在努力解决“我们现在在 7 月 25 日发布的 1.49 更新中发现了以下问题：汽车物理模拟 - 意外的车辆行为。开发人员在<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/thegranturismo/status/1816490380768199135">X 上的一篇帖子</a>中表示：“当在汽车设置中设置特定的汽车设置时就会产生这种情况。”修复应该很快就会准备好，所以请在喜剧持续时享受它。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/gran-tourismo-7s-more-realistic-physicals-update-is-launching-cars-into-orbit-120045578.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/gran-tourismo-7s-more-realistic-physics-update-is-launching-cars-into-orbit-120045578.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 54127491-53d7-4a5d-8e83-4d16dd8501f2 </guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Steve Dent]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Fri, 26 Jul 2024 12:00:45 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1721985085</ingested><modified> 2024-07-26T09:11:28+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Video Games]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Steve Dent]]></category><media:content height="764" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-07%2Fd2395a40-4b22-11ef-bc96-a1fd63022704&amp;resize=1400%2C764&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=d574a97471765a1a902d7ad6532b1