n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:3;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.engadget.com/embracer-acquires-eidos-square-enix-montreal-and-other-studios-for-300-million-091019083.html" data-original-link="https://www.engadget.com/embracer-acquires-eidos-square-enix-montreal-and-other-studios-for-300-million-091019083.html"><ins>收购</ins></a>。</p><p>本月早些时候，有消息称，一部名为<em>《凯恩的遗产：灵魂掠夺者 - 亡灵崛起》</em>的前传漫画小说正在制作中，这将是 Bit Bot 和 Crystal Dynamics 的<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:4;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/bitbotmedia/legacy-of-kain-soul-reaver-prequel-graphic-novel" data-original-link="https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/bitbotmedia/legacy-of-kain-soul-reaver-prequel-graphic-novel"><ins>Kickstarter 项目</ins></a>。</p><p>我们已就今天的泄露事件联系 Crystal Dynamics，如果收到任何官方信息，我们将更新该消息。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/comic-con-leak-sparks-rumors-of-two-remastered-soul-reaver-games-223906020.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/comic-con-leak-sparks-rumors-of-two-remastered-soul-reaver-games-223906020.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> ca2ebde9-f644-4a90-9e8a-eb6cd6993d87</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Anna Washenko]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Thu, 25 Jul 2024 22:39:07 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1721947148</ingested><modified> 2024-07-25T22:39:18+00:00</modified><category><![CDATA[Humanities]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Anna Washenko]]></category><media:content height="787" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-im